snippet.textDisplay: One of the problems with vr is sickness. There’s a terrible cognitive load between interpreting the virtual space and the physical space outside your headset that if you take it on and off you get nauseous. A feature like viewing the room with cameras then taking off the headset will make this sickness less prevalent and I’m looking forward to trying this new headset despite my poor experiences with the meta quest 2
